&quot;Athelfi, I believe it is time for you to wear the great symbol of pride for all the ancient queens of the Amazons.  In the old days, a queen was recognized by the wearing of the golden belt.  I know you have heard of the stories of these belts.  And it is time,&quot;Hipp hands it to Alysia. &quot;for you to be belted... my Queen.&quot; Hipp smirked and winked. &quot;This was crafted by Alcippe, our smithy in Themiscrya.  I know she has taken great time and pride in working on this belt for me to give to you. Wear it with pride, athelfi.&quot;<br>
Hippolyte then picked up the leather and rose from the ground...then saluted them with the clink of her guantlets.  <br>
&quot;May the Gods bless you,&quot; she nodded to Marpe who lead the stallion to the Scynthian stables.  Then she and Gabby walked away from the couple. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenmaytha.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Maytha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#993300>(4/14/01 10:58:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=116.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.chickpages.com/rants/xamznqnmayx/images/smallmaytha.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Wishes the Best</span><hr size=1> Maytha walks toward Aly and Eli. She neals down and hands out a box to them. Bows head in honor.<br>
<br>
&quot;I wish the greatest through out your marriage. And Congrats on your marriage.&quot; Maytha says as she raises her hand up, handing them the box.<br>
<br>
In the box, it has jewels all around it, and inside, has 2 rings, for the new husband and wife. To show that there love will be eternal. <p><FONT SIZE="10"><FONT FACE="WingDings">Z</FONT></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ulatraariah.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LaTra Ariah</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=C:\America Online 6.0\download\moonicon.bmp BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#993300>(4/15/01 4:34:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=116.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A symbol of growth</span><hr size=1> Ari walked forward and smiled softly.<br>
&quot;I want to wish you both the best. Alysia, since I first started your training, you have grown so much...&quot;<br>
A young Amazon girl walks forward carrying a staff a little more than half Alysia's size. Ari smiles and takes the staff, nodding thanks to the younger Amazon.<br>
&quot;This is the staff you trained with, Aly, when we first started.&quot; She knelt and placed the staff before them. &quot;I want to give this to you as a symbol. So that your marraige can continue to grow throughout the years.&quot; She smiled at Aly, then at Eli, stood and moved back to her place in the seats. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugenesistiberon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Genesis Tiberon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#993300>(4/15/01 5:30:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=116.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Blessings</span><hr size=1> Genesis moved forward to Eli and Aly, looking to them, a small slight nod. &quot;I give you both my blessings&quot; She had that stern wise look to her eyes and face, she continued..&quot;And I bring no gift, as no amount of gifts could compair to the gift of Love, be safe and well in this..bond..&quot; She looked to Aly..and gave a small smile, ALy &amp; Gen had already spoken on amny things in relation to the marriage, Aly knew where Genesis stood. She turns and walks away. <p><A HREF="http://www.monkeegirl.com/rpg" target=_blank"><IMG SRC="http://www.monkeegirl.com/genesisbanner.jpg" border="0"></A></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#993300>- </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite>Amazons Unite</a><font color=#993300> - </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6>Amazons of the Northern Lands</a> <font color=#993300> - </font><a href="http://www.amazonsunite.i-p.com">Home</a><font color=#993300> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.3 b4<br>Copyright ©1999-2001 ezboard, Inc.</center></